leaving washington dc was the worst just becasue i had met so many new people including four that will be in my life forever. dani(donny) in texas thats how they spell donny weird i know, brian, jen, and pam. pam and jen were my holiday inn roomies and brian and dani were the boys that were always in our room lol. during washington i did many amazing things that made me look at things in a different perspective. seriously.... well anyways yea from sunday the 18th till weds. the 21 those days in washington was the best four days of my life. i love you dani, brian, jen, and pam cant wait for the four of you to come down to florida and stay with me at my house
